Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:43.13,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.31,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:01.27,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:10.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:20.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:29.72,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:38.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:46.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:53.41,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:55.66,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:43.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:57.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:01.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:10.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:20.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:29.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:38.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:46.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.36,0:23:47.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.94,0:23:53.41,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:55.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.01,0:00:43.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:48.06,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:56.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:02.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:06.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.09,0:01:16.51,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.51,0:01:23.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:28.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:34.57,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:37.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.95,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.54,0:01:48.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:59.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.80,0:02:04.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
